create an automation UiPath Project using decision statements.
odd and even
Steps:
1) Create a new project.
2) Create a variable as number Int32 Main Sequence
3) Add a Input Dialog Activity 
dialog title enter “check no is even” and in 
input label type “enter any number” and 
input type “textbox” and 
value entered “number” variable with variable type int32.
4) Add a If Activity 
condition : number Mod 2=0
Then activity add a  message box
Text: “number Is even”+vbCrLf
Else activity add message box
text: “number is odd”+vbCrLf
